    "en": {
      "name": "Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Primal",
      "effect": "When a Dragon Xyz Monster declares an attack: Attach this card on the field to it as material. You can only use each of the following effects of \"Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Primal\" once per turn. If a Dragon Xyz Monster is on the field (Quick Effect): You can Special Summon this card from your hand to either field. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: Its owner adds 1 \"Tachyon\" Spell/Trap from their Deck to their hand.",
